WITH mtd_signups AS (
    SELECT 
        DATE_TRUNC('week', created_at_utc)::DATE AS week_start,
        COUNT(*) AS total_signups,
        SUM(CASE WHEN email_type = 'Professional' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS qualified_signups
    FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM
    WHERE created_at_utc >= DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE)
      AND created_at_utc < CURRENT_DATE + 1
      AND filtered_core = 'true'
    GROUP BY 1
)
SELECT 
    week_start,
    total_signups,
    qualified_signups,
    ROUND(qualified_signups * 100.0 / NULLIF(total_signups, 0), 1) AS qualified_pct
FROM mtd_signups
ORDER BY week_start

SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS total_signups_mtd
FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM
WHERE created_at_utc >= DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE)
  AND created_at_utc < CURRENT_DATE + 1
  AND filtered_core = 'true'

SELECT 
    SUM(CASE WHEN email_type = 'Professional' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS qualified_signups_mtd
FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM
WHERE created_at_utc >= DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE)
  AND created_at_utc < CURRENT_DATE + 1
  AND filtered_core = 'true'

SELECT 
    ROUND(
        100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN email_type = 'Professional' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / 
        NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0)
    , 1) AS qualified_rate_pct
FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM
WHERE created_at_utc >= DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE)
  AND created_at_utc < CURRENT_DATE + 1
  AND filtered_core = 'true'
